            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>奧多比系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADBE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADBE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADBE-US</a>)截至台北時間05日23:16股價上漲16.44美元，報345.17美元，漲幅5%，成交量1,834,679（股），盤中最高價345.17美元、最低價329.71美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.52%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.69%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.17%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>奧多比系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADBE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADBE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADBE-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.08%</li> <li>近 1 月：-2.56%</li> <li>近 3 月：-5.09%</li> <li>近 6 月：-21.05%</li> <li>今年以來：-25.9%</li></ul></section></main>",
